                           pitch ladder adopts (temporarily) the  water-
                           line  mark.  Another  feature  is the closure
                           speed which is shown under the  piper  rather
                           than  on a radar ranging scale. Optionally, a
                           pendulum (or what do you  call  it?)  can  be


